To compile the code, please, run make in this directorty.

2 programs are provided:

1) hw2_reduction: Computes the sum of a random input array of floats. Input array length called be passed as a program argument as ./hw2_reduction (INPUT_LENGTH), or otherwise, by default an array of 1048576 elements is considered.

2) hw2_reduction_multiple. It does the same as hw2_reduction, but starting from an inpput length of 512, it doubles the input length every iteration, for 10 runs.
